              <h2 style="color:#12d640">Portuguese Banking Classification</h2>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Tech Stack</strong>: Python, Scikit-Learn, Pandas, NumPy</li>
                <li><strong>Github URL</strong>: <a href="https://github.com/Bharath-2605/Portuguese-Banking-Classification" target="_blank">Project Link</a></li>
